comment: Hill (LAL) sets the screen on Dinwiddie (DET) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Drummond (DET) makes "hi-five" contact immediately after the ball has been released on the hook shot by Hill (LAL), which is legal.
Boozer (LAL) makes contact with Monroe's (DET) arm and the contact affects his shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (DET) cleanly blocks the transition layup attempt by Ellington (LAL)
RHH shows Drummond (DET) holds Lin (LAL) after he gains control of the rebound.
Lin (LAL) makes no movement toward Dinwiddie (DET) as he attempts his shot.
Drummond (DET) dislodges Hill (LAL) as he sets up to rebound.
Dinwiddie (DET) commits a take foul on Lin (LAL).
Meeks (DET) commits a take foul on Hill (LAL).
